title: Shawn McDonald Discography 2000-2013 (12 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SHAWN MCDONALD DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 12 releases...

 * 2000 - Here There And Everything In Between
 * 2002 - Focal Point
 * 2004 - Simply Nothing
 * 2005 - Live In Seattle
 * 2006 - Connect Sets EP
 * 2006 - Ripen
 * 2007 - Scattered Pieces - Live
 * 2008 - Roots
 * 2008 - Roots Remixed
 * 2011 - Closer
 * 2011 - Closer - Deluxe Edition
 * 2013 - The Analog Sessions

Shawn Michael McDonald is a Contemporary Christian music singer, songwriter and guitarist.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
